We're grateful to [The Recurse Center](https://recurse.com) for hosting us!
To help them out (and for the address), please RSVP via Luma [here](https://luma.com/zd8ul0il).

Approximate timeline:

- 10:00 – 10:30: gathering, bagels + coffee, chit-chat
- 10:30 – 11:00: explain projects, form groups, set up workstations
- 11:00 – 13:00: work on stuff together
- 13:00 – 14:30: lunch break
- 14:30 – 16:30: work on stuff together (continued)
- 16:30 – 17:00: show others what you made and what you learned
